# Performance & Accessibility

## Performance
- **React**: Use React.memo, useMemo, useCallback for expensive operations
- **Next.js**: Leverage static generation, dynamic imports, Image optimization
- **Bundle**: Code splitting, tree shaking, analyze with `npm run build`
- **PWA**: Service worker caching, preload critical resources
- **Audio**: Stream large files, implement proper buffering

## Accessibility (WCAG 2.1)
- **Semantic HTML**: Use proper heading hierarchy (h1-h6)
- **ARIA**: Labels, roles, states for complex components
- **Keyboard**: Tab navigation, focus management, escape handling
- **Screen Readers**: Alt text, descriptive labels, skip links
- **Audio Player**: Keyboard controls, transcript support, captions

## Media Queries & Responsive
- Mobile-first approach
- Test on multiple devices and screen readers
- Respect user preferences: prefers-reduced-motion, prefers-color-scheme

## Audio-Specific A11y
- Play/pause keyboard shortcuts (spacebar)
- Speed controls with clear labels
- Volume controls with ARIA live regions
- Chapter navigation support
- Resume playback position

## Core Web Vitals
- LCP < 2.5s (optimize images, fonts)
- FID < 100ms (minimize JavaScript)
- CLS < 0.1 (size images, avoid layout shifts)
